  "text": [
    "1",
    "Did I say I was a creature",
    "of habit?",
    "I meant the opposite.",
    "I meant behavior",
    "is a pile of clothes",
    "I might or might not wear.",
    "Before all the sowing and reaping",
    "could go on for centuries,",
    "before the calendar,",
    "I must have been convinced",
    "that my movements",
    "were both mandated",
    "and blessed.",
    "2",
    "I've never been an old woman",
    "knitting by a fire",
    "but I've played one",
    "in images",
    "where it meant being foolish",
    "or wise, a mistress",
    "of distraction's",
    "indirection.",
    "To rock while entwining",
    "is life's work,",
    "but I am reckless,",
    "restless"
  ],
  "title": "Life's Work",
  "year": ""
}